name: Saint Wander//The First
description:
-Accidental cult leader
-Smooth talker
-True Neutral
-Ex-interstellar pilot

"Oh, Benevolent Lucretia our one true Mother
Cleanse our tainted past and keep us away from the blackest night
Through the ever stalwart words of Wise Wander, The First of your prophet
We build a bridge to the future most pure
Where we would walk, hands united, voices as one
Until the day we return to your embrace"

- The Hymn of Lucretia

1536x2048 144dpi
